How to run APP:
cd into Student-App/angular-source
ionic serve

To run the api server: (No longer need to do as is now hosted)
cd into Student-App
nodemon index

To access the database in the shell:
/ProgramFiles/MongoDB/server/3.4/bin/
mongo "mongodb://breakpoint-shard-00-00-ti5q0.mongodb.net:27017,breakpoint-shard-00-01-ti5q0.mongodb.net:27017,breakpoint-shard-00-02-ti5q0.mongodb.net:27017/test?replicaSet=Breakpoint-shard-0" --authenticationDatabase admin --ssl --username Breakpoint --password breakpoint 

MongoDB Commands:
- show dbs 
- use breakpoint (this is this projects db)
- show collections 
- db.collectionName.find().pretty() --> Will show all entries in the collection, e.g: db.students.find().pretty()

